g.text: For SPI boot, IO9 must be high
For download boot, IO8 must be
low and IO9 must be high
The resistors on SDA and SCL both
configure boot and are pullups for I2C
SW5 and SW6 have external pullup resistors for booting
SW1 has an external pulldown resistor for booting
PCB must be 1.6mm thick for PCIe
